title: Snapped Killer Couples - Season 1
description:
Snapped Killer Couples - Season 1

Features couples whose passion drives them to commit terrible criminal acts. Through recreations and gripping firsthand accounts, each episode takes a deep dive into the stories behind the couples' romance, how their relationship evolved once love turned into manipulation and what ultimately drove them to commit the crime.

Ep 1 - Amanda Logue & Jason Andrews
Ep 2 - Jennifer Henderson & Skylar DeLeon
Ep 3 - Sarah Edmond & Ben Darras
Ep 4 - Tina Leja & Darnell Smith
Ep 5 - Tylar Witt & Steven Colver
Ep 6 - Laura Hall & Colton Pitonyak
Ep 7 - Elizabeth Turpin & Karen Brown
Ep 8 - Donna Moonda & Damien Bradford
Ep 9 - Nicole Kasinskas & Billy Sullivan
Ep 10 - Tabitha Messina & Carlos Christopher
